<node CREATED="1285154860267" ID="ID_517196004" MODIFIED="1285154874365" TEXT="`View` is the base class for widgets, which are used to create interactive UI components (buttons, text fields, etc.)."/>
<node CREATED="1285154881964" ID="ID_1150068628" MODIFIED="1285154881964" TEXT="The `ViewGroup` subclass is the base class for layouts, which are invisible containers that hold other `View`s (or other `ViewGroup`s) and define their layout properties."/>
